                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17911026-19-defend218 t17911026-19-punish112"></join>
               imprisoned six months
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. Baron HOTHAM.</p>
